Source: luks-root-smartcard-tools
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: JT <jtmoree@users.noreply.github.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/jtmoree-github-com/luks-root-smartcard

Package: luks-root-smartcard-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, cryptsetup-initramfs, initramfs-tools, gnupg, opensc, pcscd
Description: Smartcard-based LUKS root unlock for Debian/Ubuntu
 Provides an initramfs hook and boot script that decrypt the root volume
 key on a smartcard (pkcs11-tool or GPG/scdaemon) without requiring
 systemd libraries in the initrd.
